Measuring EquipmentIntroduction

We provide high-technology measurement equipment around the world to research and development institutes such as universities, national laboratories, electronics and automotive industries and all.
Additionally we support proper installation, technical training, calibration, maintenance, and repair services with advanced techniques.
*We are looking for suppliers that want to expand into Japanese and Asian market.
If you are interested, please contact us!
 
